    dc:title "And then there were six: a revision of the genus Phanolinopsis Scheerpeltz (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Staphylininae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.897337>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.897339>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.897341> ;
